EmailTemplate.subject: Your BigCommerce Store Setup
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Welcome to BigCommerce! We wanted to thank you not only for choosing BigCommerce but also for choosing to work with our professional services team to get your store up and running. We have thousands of store setups under our belt and will make the process simple (and even fun!) for you.
We will call you within one business day to get you going. Be sure to have your store login information handy for the call. We have a Statement of Work for you to review so you know what we will cover during our call - view it online here - http://www.clicktools.com/survey?iv=vsfccz8jciaj&q1={!Case.Id}
We’re looking forward to speaking with you soon!
Thank you for choosing BigCommerce! The BigCommerce Team
